<div1 type="letter">

<pb facs="nei.j4c.46.5-6_0001a" />

<note type="curatorial">Aly Collection
229-1</note>
<opener>
<dateline>Skyrim, May 24, '65</dateline>

<salute>Dear Lucile:</salute>
</opener>
<p>You said you'd write again soon, and I'm looking forward to the next word. In the meanwhile I hope everything goes well.</p>

<p>Soon we'll be through here, and then I'll be looking across the summer towards the Nebraska tour in the fall.</p>

<pb facs="nei.j4c.46.5-6_0001b"/>
<fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>

<p>We've been graduating our youngsters &#8212; Gail from Christian, Lynn from Hickman ("best actress" also "most useful member".), Erica from 8th Grade.</p>

<p>We have some new colts &#8212; such sweethearts!</p>

<p>Why do I feel a bit heartsick, I wonder? Tell me something good to hear, <hi rend="underline">please</hi>.</p>
<closer>
<salute>Affection to you, Bower, and Stewart.</salute>

<signed>John N.</signed>
</closer>

<fw type="curatorial">5</fw>

